wt.change2

Interface FlexibleChangeRequest2

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    _WTChangeRequest2, WTChangeRequest2

    @GenAsPersistable(interfaces=FlexibleChangeItem.class)
public interface FlexibleChangeRequest2
    Interface required for a change object to participate in a flexible change request association. Classes that implement this interface must also extend ChangeRequest2.



    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false

    See Also:
    FlexibleChangeItem, FlexibleChangeLink, ChangeRequest2
